// Monody-44 - PvE Boss god 1 (god-pve)
// (Fluted Barrel, Arrowhead Brake, Corkscrew Rifling), (Enhanced Battery, Accelerated Coils), (Attrition Orbs), (Controlled Burst)
//notes:Inspired by @Saint_Kabr, @CourtProjects and @ImpetusAlways (PvE PvE-Boss PvE-BurstDamage PvE-EndGame PvE-God M+KB Controller): First-choice PvE roll for burst DPS against Banes, Elites, Champions or Minibosses, or shorter boss DPS windows in both general at-level or better, and end-game underleveled content. Monody-44 is a high-impact fusion rifle, which are rated B-Tier for endgame PvE by @TheAegisRelic tiering spreadsheet https://linktr.ee/TheAegisRelic being a big total damage outlier, and very underrated. The frame intrinsic provides ×0.8 accuracy cone size and ×0.83 accuracy cone growth when stationary or moving less than 2.8m/s (crouch walking) and ADS as per the https://www.destiny2.science/ Destiny Data Compendium. The stats are good by comparison with its peer - hopefully when the website's back https://d2foundry.gg/w/3201200906 will show how the weapon stats impact in-game performance. Use the barrel perk to boost Handling, and  the battery perk to improve Charge Time or boost battery size. There aren't any trait perks that help with reloading or refilling the battery in a boss fight, so you're best option in the first trait perk column is Attrition Orbs, which will at least drop a power orb after you've emptied your battery to keep ammo mods charged. In the second column, Controlled Burst reduces charge time to ×0.9 and boosts damage by ×1.2 for 2s (2.5s when enhanced) after landing all the bolts in a burst, or a kill. Situationally, you might also consider Surrounded to boost damage by up to to ×1.4 (×1.47 enhanced) while within 15m of 3+ enemies. The Suros Synergy origin trait is useful, granting +30 Handling and ×1.2 flinch resistance for 6s after reloading. If you're interested, a monody is an ode sung by one voice (as in a Greek tragedy) or an elegy or dirge performed by one person. Recommended MW: Charge Time, with an enhanced Charge Time mod or your preferred choice of mod to boost weapon stats, ammo generation, or elemental pickups for builds - and don't forget to check any available seasonal fragile mods.|tags:PvE PvE-Boss PvE-BurstDamage PvE-EndGame PvE-God M+KB Controller
